F(n)=F(-n)
n
f(x)=f(-x)
x
\mathcal{F}
 F(n)=F(-n)\rightarrow \int_{-\pi}^\pi f(x) e^{inx}dx=\int_{-\pi}^\pi f(x) e^{-inx}dx =\int_{-\pi}^\pi f(-x) e^{inx}dx,  
 \int_{-\pi}^\pi[f(x)-f(-x)]e^{inx}dx = 0. 
 0=\mathcal{F}[f(x)-f(-x)]\rightarrow\mathcal{F}[f(x)] = \mathcal{F}[f(-x)]. 
